reviewText: Gave one to a friend.  It was well produced, easy to follow and instructive.
Love this!! Learned some great techniques!!
The video is thorough and enjoyable to watch.  It demonstrates good techniques for the "avid skincare therapist."  I recommend this video.

I really enjoy facial massage and I decided to learn how to do it by reading some articles over the internet... but unfortunately I was not good enough. After reviewing this DVD I can honestly say that I have improved my technique and now everybody are happy when I give them a facial massage.
